title: Web Application - Personal Portfolio
description:
Created a responsive personal website to display web development projects and skills.
Built with HTML, CSS, Bootstrap,TypeScript and Angular.
It includes sections for projects, skills, and contact details,
showcasing technical expertise and professional accomplishments.

title: Mobile Application - DUAT
description:
Developed a mobile application using Flutter that assists tourists in exploring Egypt,
Integrated AI and third-party APIs functionalities to personalize travel recommendations, significantly
enhancing user engagement and providing real-time information

title: 3D Skull Landmark Detection Using DICOM Files
description:
Built a custom dataset of 3D skull X-rays with
annotated coordinates for 29 key anatomical landmarks in each
DICOM file. Developed a lightweight 3D CNN
model using TensorFlow and Keras to predict these landmarks.

title: Web Application - Gazar Foods
description: Designed and developed an interactive and user-friendly web platform for Gazar Foods, The application allows customers to personalize their meal plans, manage user profiles, and efficiently track orders in real-time, enhancing the overall customer experience and operational efficiency
